1️. ETL vs ELT (VERY IMPORTANT)
ETL:
Extract -> Transform -> Load
ELT:
Extract -> Load -> Transform => Modern companies prefer ELT

2️. Pipeline Architecture
-> Batch pipelines
- Runs every few hours
Example: daily reports

-> Real-time pipelines
- Runs continuously
Example:
- stock prices
- Uber tracking

